quirement for external network/subprocess; local persistence-backed queue is enough.","test_description":"Instantiate the real persistent queue with a small configured capacity, enqueue up to limit, then attempt one more enqueue. Assert over-capacity enqueue is rejected and persisted count never exceeds configured limit.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":"Requires real queue module + persistence integration, no higher infra needed.","level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.05,"Integration":0.7,"System":0.25,"Agentic":0.0,"Workflow":0.0}}]}
